    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to reduce the length of drainage using a treatment protocol to
      control the manipulation of the applied vacuum to the pleural cavity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this prospective study, a treatment algorithm is tested in a subgroup of patients with
      postoperative pulmo-pleural fistula. The primary aim is to reduce the duration of
      pulmo-pleural fistulation. Secondary aim is to reduce the duration of chest tube therapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
